  <front>
   <head>Las tablas del bajel despedazadas</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1" met="-+---+---+-" line_length="11">Las tablas del bajel despedazadas</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+-+-++-+-" line_length="10">(signum naufragii pium et crudele),</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+-+---+-+-" line_length="11">del tempio sacro con le rote vele,</l>
     <l n="4" met="--++-+---+-" line_length="11">ficaraon nas paredes penduradas.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2">
     <l n="5" met="-+---+---+-" line_length="11">Del tiempo las injurias perdonadas,</l>
     <l n="6" met="+-+-+--+--+-" line_length="12">et Orionis vi nimbosae stellae</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+----+---+-" line_length="12">raccoglio le smarrite pecorelle</l>
     <l n="8" met="+-+--+---+-" line_length="11">nas ribeiras do Betis espalhadas.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3">
     <l n="9" met="--++-+---+-" line_length="11">Volveré a ser pastor, pues marinero</l>
     <l n="10" met="+++++++-+--+-" line_length="13">quel Dio non vuol, che col suo strale sprona</l>
     <l n="11" met="+--+---++-+-" line_length="12">do Austro os assopros e do Oceam as agoas,</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4">
     <l n="12" met="-+-+-+---+-" line_length="11">haciendo al triste son, aunque grosero,</l>
     <l n="13" met="++-+-+-+-+-" line_length="11">di questa canna, già selvaggia donna,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+++-+-+--+-" line_length="12">saudade a as feras, e aos penedos, magoas.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
